headline: Why Lululemon (LULU) Stock Is Down Today
summary: Shares of athletic apparel retailer Lululemon (NASDAQ:LULU) fell 3.2% in the afternoon session after investors took some profits off the table as markets awaited signals on future monetary policy from the Federal Reserve's Jackson Hole symposium later in the week.
